---
// src/components/sections/Mistakes.astro
---
<section class="py-5 px-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
  <div class="text-center mb-16">
    <span class="text-indigo-600 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.2em] uppercase mb-4 block">Avoid These</span>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-800 tracking-tight">Common Mistakes and <span class="text-indigo-600">How to Fix Them</span></h2>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    {[
      { 
        num: "01", 
        title: "Treating Your Journal Like a To-Do List", 
        desc: "Recording tasks is useful, but if that's all you do, you're missing most of what journaling is designed for. It's about reflection, not just management.", 
        fix: "End every practical entry with 'How I feel about all of this is...'" 
      },
      { 
        num: "02", 
        title: "Writing What You Think You Should Feel", 
        desc: "Journaling for an imagined audience kills the authenticity that makes it work. If you're performing, you're not processing.", 
        fix: "Start with 'What I'm not saying in this journal is...'" 
      }
    ].map(m => (
      /* Card with smooth transition and scale effect */
      <div class="group relative bg-white p-8 md:p-10 rounded-[32px] border border-slate-100 shadow-sm transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-rose-500/5 hover:-translate-y-1">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start gap-8">
          <!-- Number Badge with Hover Animation -->
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <span class="bg-rose-50 text-rose-500 font-bold w-12 h-12 flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl text-sm transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:rotate-[10deg] group-hover:bg-rose-100">
              {m.num}
            </span>
          </div>

          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3 transition-colors group-hover:text-rose-600">{m.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8 group-hover:text-slate-500 transition-colors">{m.desc}</p>
            
            <!-- Solution/Fix Box -->
            <div class="inline-flex items-start md:items-center gap-3 bg-emerald-50/40 text-emerald-700 text-sm font-medium px-5 py-3 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-100/50 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:bg-emerald-50 group-hover:border-emerald-200">
               <span class="bg-emerald-500 text-white text-[10px] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-md uppercase font-black">Fix</span>
               <span class="italic">"{m.fix}"</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Decorative corner accent -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-24 h-24 bg-rose-50/30 rounded-bl-full -mr-12 -mt-12 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Optional: Smooth cursor transition */
  .group {
    cursor: pointer;
  }
</style>